Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends},
         ${misc:Depends},
         rsyslog (= ${binary:Version})
Description: Kubernetes metadata support for rsyslog
 These plugins allow rsyslog to augment syslog messages with Kubernetes
 metadata.
